<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(0deg, #E1FFF1 0%, rgba(251, 253, 255, 0.47) 100%);
        }

        .header {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .order-details {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .order-item {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .grey-line {
            border-top: 1px solid #FFF;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .image {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
        }

        .product-details {
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: top;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .title-label {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .grey-color {
            color: rgba(0, 0, 0, .7);
        }

        .line-md {
            line-height: 20px;
        }

        .size-md {
            font-size: 18px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <p class="size-md">Dear {{customerName}},</p>
            <p class="grey-color line-md">Thank you for choosing Distinguished Society for your latest fashion
                purchase! We are excited to confirm your order and provide you with the following details:</p>
        </div>

        <div class="order-details">
            <p><strong>Order Number:</strong> {{orderNumber}}</p>
            <p><strong>Order Date:</strong> {{orderDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Estimated Shipping Date:</strong> Within 2-3 business days</p>

            <h2 class="title-label">Shipping Information:</h2>
            <p><strong>Domestic Orders:</strong> Expected delivery within 6-7 business days</p>
            <p><strong>International Orders:</strong> Expected delivery within 12-15 business days</p>
            <br>
            <p><strong>Coupon Details:</strong></p>
            <p><strong>Coupon Code: {{couponCode}}</strong></p>
            <p><strong>discount:</strong>{{currCode}} {{discount}}</p>
                
            <h2 class="title-label">Order Details:</h2>
            {{#each orderItems}}
            <div class="order-item">
                <a href={{this.productName}} target="_blank"><img class="image" src={{this.productImage}} alt={{this.productTitle}}></a>
                <div class="product-details">
                    <p><strong>Product:</strong> <a href={{this.productName}} target="_blank">{{this.productTitle}}</a></p>
                    <p class="grey-color"><strong>Quantity:</strong> {{this.quantity}}</p>
                    <p><strong>Price:</strong> {{currCode}} {{this.price}} each</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
        </div>

        <div class="grey-line"></div>

        <div class="line-md grey-color">
            <p>Please note that the estimated delivery times are approximate and may vary depending on your location.
                We will provide you with a tracking number once your order has been shipped, so you can monitor its
                progress.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions or need further assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our customer
                support team at {{customerSupportEmail}} or {{customerSupportPhone}}.</p>

            <p>Thank you for being a part of the Distinguished Society. We hope you enjoy your new items!</p>
        </div>

        <div class="line-md grey-color">
            <p>Best regards,<br>
                {{yourName}}<br>
                Distinguished Society Customer Support</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
